---
title: "Line 6 PowerCab Plus - Speaker Automation"
author: "MIDI Markdown Examples"
description: |
  Demonstrates Line 6 PowerCab Plus MIDI control including speaker model switching,
  microphone simulation, mode changes, and real-time parameter automation.

  WHAT IS POWERCAB?
  PowerCab Plus is a smart powered FRFR speaker with onboard DSP for speaker modeling,
  microphone simulation, and impulse response loading. Designed for guitar modelers
  like Helix, but also works with tube amps and analog pedals.

  THREE OPERATING MODES:
  - Flat Mode: Full-range flat response (FRFR) for modelers
  - Speaker Mode: 13 classic guitar speaker models with 16 microphone simulations
  - IR Mode: User-loaded impulse responses (128 slots)

  This example demonstrates:
  - Preset recall via Program Change
  - Real-time speaker/mic changes via Control Change
  - Classic amp-speaker pairings
  - Mode switching and parameter automation
  - Integration techniques with Helix and third-party controllers

ppq: 480
tempo: 120
default_channel: 1
default_velocity: 100
